{"tid":139001,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"葛斯患代謝疾病 多蒙特：無限期休戰","createTime":"2017-03-01T05:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T08:22:43.000Z","uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c586276f4570b87f498844767ae0e3b423d94a8","tid":139001,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:15:50.000Z","msg":"德甲勁旅多蒙特於官網發表聲明，指陣中球星馬里奧葛斯因代謝疾病而需要休戰，暫時未有復出時間表；葛斯本人則表明會盡一切努力盡快復出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據「蜜蜂軍團」的聲明，葛斯近月都受肌肉問題困擾，在詳細檢查下發現根源為代謝疾病，需即時停止訓練：「多蒙特中場葛斯需要休戰。這名世界冠軍隊成員近月都受肌肉問題困擾，而進一步檢查後發現為代謝疾病，必須即時停止訓練。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然沒有明確的復出時間表，不過葛斯本人仍保持樂觀，指自己會爭取盡早復出：「我正接受治療，一定會盡可能重投訓練，助球隊達成目標。」（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a56d5bf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"9e877192aca348e17113144b0fdd573e0758eaba","tid":139001,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"afe793712e67d0698fe2faf847d9654e5e331ec9","tid":139001,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"收山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ea46b5f0aba61acb677d7c9da5aeba5c2e0510","tid":139001,"uid":31017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:27:50.000Z","msg":"傷多過踢<br />\n真係有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1083a2ed95319ee2b631c8785558588f08ce5009","tid":139001,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:27:52.000Z","msg":"成世最錯就係去左拜仁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fbeab0e90923037317dc5f4e335a8c24b8482d","tid":139001,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:29:06.000Z","msg":"唔黎代替謝拉特既後果"},{"pid":"90f26aa8afc8a2230ba679403cd65ccc58730c73","tid":139001,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":